  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p>Effective Date: April 29, 2025</p>

  <p><strong>My Notes</strong> is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when using our app.</p>

  <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> We do not collect personally identifiable information unless you contact us directly.</li>
    <li><strong>Note Content:</strong> All your notes are stored locally on your device unless you choose to back them up through third-party services (e.g., Google Drive).</li>
    <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Anonymous usage statistics may be collected to improve app performance and user experience.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
  <p>We use collected data to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Enhance app functionality and user experience</li>
    <li>Fix bugs and improve app stability</li>
    <li>Respond to user support requests</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>3. Data Sharing</h2>
  <p>We do not sell, rent, or share your personal data with third parties. Your notes and personal data remain confidential.</p>

  <h2>4. Data Security</h2>
  <p>We take appropriate security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access. However, we recommend enabling device-level protection (e.g., screen lock, encryption).</p>

  <h2>5. Third-Party Services</h2>
  <p>Some features (e.g., cloud backup or ads) may involve third-party services. Please refer to their privacy policies for more information.</p>

  <h2>6. Childrenâ€™s Privacy</h2>
  <p>My Notes is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal data from children.</p>

  <h2>7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
  <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Updates will be posted within the app and take effect immediately upon publication.</p>

  <h2>8. Contact Us</h2>
  <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:</p>
  <p>Email: <a href="mailto:higjhtech@gmail.com">higjhtech@gmail.com</a></p>

  <p>Thank you for using My Notes.</p>
